org.locationtech.geowave.analytic.clustering

Interface CentroidManager<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of item that is used to represent a centroid.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CentroidManagerGeoWave

    public interface CentroidManager<T>
    Manage centroids created per batch and per group of analytic processes. There can be multiple groups per batch. A group is loosely interpreted as a set of item geometries under analysis. The sets can be defined by shared characteristics.
